room_title: Escape room "Eat or Be Eaten" by Escape In Time in Madison
review: I took my daughter and three of her friends to "Eat or be Eaten" and we had a great time! Definitely plan to go again!

room_title: Escape room "Eat or Be Eaten" by Escape In Time in Madison
review: We did the "Eat or be Eaten" room and it was awesome to say the least! Some things came to us easily while other clues were more difficult to solve. We had a ton of fun, and we will DEFINITELY be going back in the near future!

room_title: Escape room "Eat or Be Eaten" by Escape In Time in Madison
review: First timers here. We had so much fun! Can't wait to try the other rooms. I highly recommend the eat or be eaten serial killer room.

room_title: Escape room "Eat or Be Eaten" by Escape In Time in Madison
review: We did "Eat or Be Eaten" today. Was our first ever escape room and we were paired with 3 others who it was their first time as well. We had a great time and the room look and feel was great. Would definitely go back. Thanks for the good times.

room_title: Escape room "Eat or Be Eaten" by Escape In Time in Madison
review: This was our 3rd visit. We had a group of 6 adults and loved the Eat or be Eaten room! It was the toughest we've done so far and loved it! Definitely glad for the clues... Can't wait to return for another adventure!
